Class SimplePOSResult09

All Implemented Interfaces:
Plugin, PosProcessor
public class SimplePOSResult09
extends java.lang.Object
implements PosProcessor

This plug-in changes the detailed POS tagging results to be simple. The KAIST tag set has 69 morpheme tags but this plug-in uses only 9 tags:

N(체언), P(용언), M(수식언), I(독립언), J(관계언), E(어미), X(접사), S(기호), F(외국어)

It is a POS Processor plug-in which is a supplement plug-in of phase 3 in HanNanum work flow.

Author:
Sangwon Park (hudoni@world.kaist.ac.kr), CILab, SWRC, KAIST
